{
  "$description": "Verdant handoff pack — ComponentSpecs (machine head + prose sections), DataContracts (JSON Schema 2020-12), and the DTCG token source with css/ios/android builds. Verdant is a fictional demo scenario. Generated by agent-layer/gen-handoff.mjs from system/specs/ — do not edit.",
