      "sections": [
        {
          "title": "Usage",
          "body": "Component of the Verdant demo scenario (fictional product). The screen's one committing action: full-width accent fill at the bottom of the content — on the today screen, \"Log care\" commits the checked care-task-rows. One per screen, always last in reading order; anything less than the screen's primary action is not this component. Presentational: the composing screen owns what \"commit\" means and when `disabled` lifts."
